      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, qualitative mapping of validation input parameters to COU input parameters is sufficient; quantitative equivalency metrics are not required.",
      "rationale": "A qualitative parameter mapping table confirms that the five validation operating points span the COU operating envelope. Quantitative equivalency distance metrics are not required at MRL 2 and have not been computed."
