    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels at MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. CFD-predicted NIH values agree with FDA inter-laboratory experimental data within two standard deviations at all five operating points, and the relative hemolysis index RH is below the acceptance criterion of 1.0 relative to the predicate device across the full COU operating envelope. The assessment package is submitted under ProfileMinimal; a digital signature will be appended upon completion of the institutional signature workflow. The absence of a signature at this stage is a known procedural gap and does not affect the technical credibility conclusions.",
